Not only was this a successful project, but we managed to host this server, and got to Page 1 of google, with a Maximum hit of 153 Players Online, the server Load was only at roughly 25%.. Pretty much means this server could hold around a good 600-700 Players Depending on your VPS.
The reason why we have decide to release this is that we have grown tired and we had all of the fun from this project that there possibly was to of been had, it has been a great learning experience, and now it is time to give back to the community so other people can have as much fun with this as we did.[/I]
